# External checkouts and stale worktrees — NOT part of the TTS Lab source.
# These inflate pi-lens/LSP diagnostics with upstream third-party code that is
# not our responsibility to fix. Excluding them keeps src/ and tests/ as the
# only diagnostic surface for this repo.
comfyui/
.worktrees/

